# Web (Ops UI)

- Stack: Vite, React, TypeScript strict, Tailwind
- Read-only: no business decisions; no direct DB / Playwright / n8n
- All data via Backend `/api/*`
- Pages: Queue (`ApplyJob` table), Applications (`Application` + vacancy table)
- Cover letter: modal on click; second click / Esc / backdrop closes
- Prefer TanStack Query for list + polling; thin `api/` client
- No secrets in frontend; env only for API base URL if needed
- Keep structure small: `api/`, `pages/`, `components/`, `types/`
